-- Buffett says: "We're in a recession": CNBC
-- 
-- Mon Mar 3, 2008 7:04am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/03/us-buffett-recession-idUSWEN425920080303

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Warren Buffett, chief executive of Berkshire Hathaway Inc ( BRKa.N ) ( BRKb.N ), said on Monday that "from a common sense standpoint right now, we're in a recession." 

 Speaking on CNBC, Buffett said the United States might not be in a recession from a technical standpoint, but based on what he sees from the businesses Berkshire Hathaway manages, the economy is contracting. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins ; Editing by Lisa Von Ahn)